            "நீதிமன்ற விரிவாக்கம்"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Article 21A – Right to Education",
        "points": {
          "en": [
            "Free education (6–14 years)",
            "Added by 86th Amendment",
            "Fundamental duty link"
